sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    actor Client
    participant Frontend as Frontend React
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant Event as Event Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Admin->>Frontend: Consulte les demandes d'événements
    Frontend->>Gateway: GET /api/events (admin)
    Gateway->>Event: Proxy requête (rôle ADMIN vérifié)
    Event->>DB: SELECT events WHERE status = PENDING
    DB-->>Event: Demandes en attente
    Event-->>Frontend: {events[]}
    Frontend-->>Admin: Liste des demandes

    Admin->>Frontend: Prépare un devis
    Note right of Frontend: Sélectionne plats, quantités,<br/>fixe prix, ajoute message
    Frontend->>Gateway: POST /api/quotes
    Note right of Frontend: {eventId, items[], totalPrice, message}
    Gateway->>Event: Proxy requête
    Event->>DB: INSERT INTO quotes (status: SENT)
    Event->>DB: UPDATE event SET status = QUOTED
    DB-->>Event: Devis créé
    Event-->>Frontend: {quote}
    Frontend-->>Admin: "Devis envoyé"

    Note over Admin,DB: Le client reçoit le devis

    Client->>Frontend: Consulte ses événements
    Frontend->>Gateway: GET /api/events/:id
    Gateway->>Event: requête
    Event->>DB: SELECT event + quotes
    Event-->>Frontend: {event, quotes[]}
    Frontend-->>Client: Affiche devis reçu

    alt Client accepte
        Client->>Frontend: Clique "Accepter"
        Frontend->>Gateway: PATCH /api/quotes/:id/accept
        Gateway->>Event: Proxy
        Event->>DB: UPDATE quote SET status = ACCEPTED
        Event->>DB: UPDATE event SET status = CONFIRMED
        Event-->>Frontend: Confirmé
    else Client refuse
        Client->>Frontend: Clique "Refuser"
        Frontend->>Gateway: PATCH /api/quotes/:id/reject
        Gateway->>Event: Proxy
        Event->>DB: UPDATE quote SET status = REJECTED
        Event-->>Frontend: Refusé
    end
